Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.91,0:00:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.54,0:00:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.66,0:00:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not uncommon to see students skipping class\Non the rooftop in manga and such,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you actually took a nap up there,\Nyou'd get a sunburn like no other.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.00,0:00:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I think third period is about\Nto start for everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.62,0:00:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I pretty much always skipped classes,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.91,0:00:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and Adachi rarely ever came to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.62,0:00:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We happened to meet up here by chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:01:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and ended up spending a lot of time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you mind if I serve next?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.04,0:01:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.50,0:01:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.87,0:01:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.12,0:01:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I found out how to do that serve online.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.37,0:01:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't have a racket at home,\Nso I practiced with a rice paddle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.70,0:01:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No fair using curveballs on amateurs like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.33,0:01:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You lack ambition, young Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.12,0:01:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's not my... fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.50,0:01:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,When we're skipping class like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.08,0:01:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--we can usually sense if the other is here.\N--I can only get it to work like\None out of ten times right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--And we usually find each other up here.\N--So you're getting worse...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.16,0:01:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess third period was PE class.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What if they come up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.04,0:01:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we open the windows and jump?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:02:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! But we're on the second floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't we break our legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I see that you lack calcium in your diet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.08,0:02:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't like that interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.12,0:02:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap. This is sorta exciting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think they realize\Nwe're up here, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll just drink some milk\Nwith my lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.08,0:02:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So my legs don't break if we ever have to jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you've decided\Nto strengthen your bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This time we spent together\Nwhere nothing else mattered
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,always felt so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh... Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.62,0:04:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I can't anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.87,0:04:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost lunchtime anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how lewd. Our school's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:53.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.87,0:04:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Dignity?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that! Our school's dignity\Nis at stake here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's lunchtime, but what should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.00,0:05:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah. We can't have you\Ngo out in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.16,0:05:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.41,0:05:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I always seem to have\Ndifferent opinions about "next time."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you probably want your usual danish,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.16,0:05:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,but do you want milk today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.75,0:05:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Water, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Doing bad things with Adachi is pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it because I got hooked\Ndoing this with Adachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.25,0:05:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,or do I just get a rush doing bad things?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer's obvious, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.50,0:05:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave things ambiguous for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she even doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:06:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura was the first one to be up here\Non the second floor of the gymnasium.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.62,0:06:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She still looked like a middle schooler,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,so I figured she was a first-year like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Adachi, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, we're in the same class.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.25,0:06:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,My nickname's Shimamura, but in hiragana.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.58,0:06:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.33,0:06:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I just happened to stop by today.\NWhat about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Pretty much the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They're so loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.16,0:06:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:06:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.95,0:07:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you able to touch them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.70,0:07:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Cicadas aren't too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Think it'll stay on?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How many days do you think it has left?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.58,0:07:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.20,0:07:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.87,0:07:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer do you want it to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.87,0:07:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen days... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.50,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifteen days later,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura's hands were covered in dirt\Nwhen she came up to the second floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.66,0:07:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That was my first encounter with Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.58,0:07:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:08:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you the last danish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.08,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your water.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.70,0:08:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,This was still when
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.25,0:08:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't consider Shimamura my friend yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.37,0:08:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Tea"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.41,0:08:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeak, squeak, squeak, squeak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Pshuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Learning Table Tennis From Zero"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess they have a book for everything.\NDang, that's expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.12,0:08:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha lookin' at?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,--Smash! You joining the table\Ntennis club, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hino is a classmate\Nwho's sort of a plain jane.\N--Smash! You joining the table\Ntennis club, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hino is a classmate\Nwho's sort of a plain jane.\N--No, I was just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.58,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,--She's never even dyed her hair before.\N--No, I was just curious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.50,0:08:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,--She's never even shoplifted, either.\N--Curious? You randomly picked\Na book about ping-pong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,--She's apparently never pulled the hair\Nof a girl from another school, either.\N--Curious? You randomly picked\Na book about ping-pong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.41,0:08:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.95,0:08:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--Jeez. You just leave me behind\Nand end up finding Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:09:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,--My other classmate, Nagafuji, is your\Nusual bespectacled girl with big boobs.\N--Jeez. You just leave me behind\Nand end up finding Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,--Need I say more?\N--Jeez. You just leave me behind\Nand end up finding Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.62,0:09:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,--Need I say more?\N--So, what were you\Ntalking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.29,0:09:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,--Her big boobs and her big attitude\Nmake her pretty mature...\N--Nothing important.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.00,0:09:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,--All right. I won't inquire any further then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,--...but she's a bit dumb.\N--All right. I won't inquire any further then.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.20,0:09:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hino, do you have an excuse\Nfor that blatant sexual harassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagafuji is too self-conscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.87,0:09:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought I'd lighten the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.95,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.41,0:09:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when they're this big,\Nthe boys always look.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure all the boys in class\Nstaring at your boobies
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.12,0:09:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,have fondled them at least\Nten times in their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.20,0:09:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! That's gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.16,0:09:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the price you pay for being famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, whoops. My hand slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.16,0:09:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Hino and Nagafuji\Nhave been friends since they were little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I became friends with them\Nafter we got into high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.20,0:09:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,so my distance with them varies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But when it comes to distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:10:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,being as close as you can be\Nisn't always the best option.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you get too close, you might fight\Nand have misunderstandings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. The other day at the fishing hole\Nthere was someone in a spacesuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.04,0:10:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think relationships with others
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:46.37,Default,,0,0,0,,are like free diving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.41,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, who was that?\NWasn't she in our class in like April?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that like every time we see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Her name is Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.45,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,She's our classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She's definitely a certified delinquent.\NTeacher-approved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.08,0:11:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.50,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she one of yours, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep sinking deeper and deeper,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and things start disappearing around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.08,0:11:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You struggle to breathe, so you try\Nto get back to the water's surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you poke your head out\Nfor a breath of air
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.87,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,before sinking deeper yet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.20,0:12:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,If you keep repeating that cycle...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you're late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.95,0:12:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...thought I'd just head home,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.37,0:12:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,but I heard the sound of a ping-pong ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.45,0:12:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.70,0:12:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.58,0:12:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your school bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.91,0:12:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,In my bicycle's basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm heading home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.66,0:13:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Let's go to class today,"\Nor "Let's walk home together today."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.75,0:13:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Which would you prefer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.29,0:13:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case... I'll just go kill some time\Nsomewhere until school's over... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.33,0:13:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't have to be sitting\Nthe same exact way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it started raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the rain's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.25,0:13:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way is your house, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.91,0:13:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, hold this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I just figured your house\Nwas pretty far from mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.83,0:13:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I live this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.75,0:14:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So, whose home\Nshould we go home to first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a novel way of putting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.95,0:14:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Why don't we go to your place first?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Riding a bike like this is a crime, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that matters. We're delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.83,0:14:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, being delinquents rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.41,0:14:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I guess you actually have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean Hino and Nagafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were always up there\Nbecause you didn't have friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.16,0:14:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What about you, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably my only one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.29,0:14:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.70,0:15:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Killing time outside of school\Nand then going home together is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This is definitely weird,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,but the idea sounded amusing and elating.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,If either of us were actually\Nhonor students, we'd say,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.45,0:15:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"We shouldn't be doing this!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And try to steer the other back down\Nthe right path with the power of friendship,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.16,0:15:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but we were both pretty irresponsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.70,0:15:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So we were just dragging\Neach other down deeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.25,0:15:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I go through here, and then...\Nto get back to my house...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty decent walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I got you a towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wh-Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel bad for making you take\Na really long way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.45,0:15:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Want me to give you a ride home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.00,0:16:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No. This whole ride\Nwould be pointless, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.95,0:16:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll probably see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.04,0:16:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When I looked down at Adachi's head\Nfrom the back of her bicycle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.50,0:16:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed her hair that usually\Nlooked so pretty with her face
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,also looked like some floofy creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I looked the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weird day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.45,0:16:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,See? I told you there were noises\Ncoming from upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I guess you really were\Nplaying table tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.75,0:16:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Gack.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really say, "Gack" to your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.54,0:17:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.62,0:17:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how'd you know I was here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.58,0:17:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You were looking at the table tennis\Nbook at the bookstore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.25,0:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoopsie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So... Is that Adachi over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I think that's pretty\Nself-explanatory, but yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.45,0:17:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys were friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then yesterday... Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Nagafuji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.33,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagafuji and Hino... Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I bought us some bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.58,0:17:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised they never found\Nyou guys during PE class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.04,0:17:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We stayed pretty quiet\Nwhenever there was class.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.54,0:18:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one do you want, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.04,0:18:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take whichever one you like, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... In that case... Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.70,0:18:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you free on Sunday, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.83,0:18:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This week? I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.95,0:18:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then wanna go to the fishing hole?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.12,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid in the spacesuit\NI was telling you about is a riot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you basically just asking me\Nto go fishing with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. That's just a bonus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They said they wanted to meet you\Nwhen I mentioned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just take Nagafuji with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I have club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm... Yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.62,0:18:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.25,0:18:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're going to the fishing hole on Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The next day, Adachi didn't come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.54,0:18:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a lot\NI didn't know about Adachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:19:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and that frustrated me at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.66,0:19:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What I did know was what I felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,After seeing Hino and Nagafuji having\Na blast up here yesterday, I realized again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.91,0:19:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi might not show up again for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was super unlucky, I may not\Nsee her again until graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That was totally possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.91,0:19:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess my luck does suck. Welp...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.41,0:19:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Blammo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.29,0:19:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I was planning to stop\Nbut didn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.12,0:19:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I heard you say, "Blammo."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.70,0:20:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your house isn't this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.29,0:20:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.91,0:20:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.41,0:20:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.25,0:20:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Eggy Bread"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.70,0:20:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was going to give them\Nto you during lunch today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.00,0:20:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so this is "next time."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you weren't going home\Nwith your other friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.25,0:20:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have been able\Nto give them to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.87,0:20:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi had said that I was her only friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.04,0:20:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess that's all there is to it then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This was about all I could ask
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.75,0:20:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and this was all Adachi\Nwas able to say right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.16,0:20:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.29,0:20:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You are walking me all the way home, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that was my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.50,0:21:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at me! I'm a plane! Vroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.58,0:21:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The slight elation that I felt\Nhad given me wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.95,0:21:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how many steps it'll take\Nbefore embarrassment sets in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's Adachi like?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.70,0:23:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she like? Um, normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains nothing,\Nmy dear Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.00,0:23:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how much I should tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.25,0:23:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi likes water\Nand usually drinks mineral water.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.54,0:23:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem to care about brands.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.25,0:23:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So Adachi is a Namekian.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.87,0:23:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen her regrow\Nany limbs yet, though. Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.62,0:23:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything biting?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.87,0:23:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh... Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.45,0:23:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The spacesuit was so white that it just\Ncompounded their awkward presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.95,0:23:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly, a small astronaut stood before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.16,0:23:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 1: Playing Ping-Pong in Our Uniforms"\NSuddenly, a small astronaut stood before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.58,0:23:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 1: Playing Ping-Pong in Our Uniforms"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.87,0:24:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Adachi Question'"\NAdashimapedia: Ping-Pong!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.45,0:24:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Adachi Question'"\NExplain the difference between\Ntable tennis and ping-pong.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Adachi Question'"\NWhen you're playing seriously,\Nit's table tennis. Ping-pong is just for fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.62,0:24:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,--But what about when you play\Nping-pong seriously?\N--Then it's table tennis.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.66,0:24:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,--But what about table tennis for fun?\N--Then it's just ping-pong!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.83,0:24:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ping-pong is but table tennis.\N--Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.91,0:24:12.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to sound philosophical.

